quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  27,45,"A Thamoud, ndithudi, tidawatumizira m’bale wawo Saleh, amene adati, “Muzipembedza Mulungu basi.” Koma iwo adagawikana m’magulu awiri okangana"
  27,46,"Iye adati, “Anthu anga! Kodi bwanji mufuna kubweretsa choipa msanga musanabweretse chabwino? Nanga ndi chifukwa chiyani simupempha chikhululukiro kwa Mulungu kuti mukhoza kupeza chisomo chake?”"
  27,47,"Iwo adati, “Ife tili kuona choipa chochokera kwa iwe ndiponso kwa anthu amene amakutsatira iwe.” Iye adati, “Choipa chimene muli kuchiona chili kuchokera kwa Mulungu. Inu ndinu anthu amene muli kuyesedwa.”"
  27,48,M’mizinda mwawo mudali anthu asanu ndi anayi amene anali kuchita zoipa mdziko ndipo samachita zabwino ayi
  27,49,"Iwo adati, “Tiyeni tonse tilumbire, dzina la Mulungu, kuti timuphe nthawi ya usiku pamodzi ndi a pabanja lake lonse. Ndipo tidzawauza abale ake kuti, “Ife kudalibe pamene iwo anali kuphedwa. Ndipo zimene tili kunena ndi zoona zokhazokha.”"
  27,50,Iwo adachita chiwembu ndipo nafenso tidachita chiwembu iwo osadziwa chilichonse
  27,51,Ndipo taona zotsatira zake za chiwembu chawo. Ife tidawaonongeratu pamodzi ndi anthu awo onse
  27,52,"Chifukwa chakuti iwo adalakwa, nyumba zawo zimene anali kukhalamo tsopano ndi mabwinja. Ndithudi m’zimenezi muli zizindikiro kwa anthu ozindikira"
  27,53,Ndipo Ife tidapulumutsa anthu onse okhulupirira ndipo anali kuopa Mulungu
  27,54,"Loti kwa anthu ake, “Kodi inu mukuchita zinthu zochititsa manyazi pamene muli kuona?”"
  27,55,“Kodi inu muli kuchita chiwerewere ndi amuna anzanu pokwaniritsa zilakolako zanu ndi kusiya akazi? Inu ndinu mbuli basi.”